<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Disclosures | Time Investment Advisers LLC</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Time Investment Advisers LLC — independent investment advisory services focused on disciplined long-term guidance.">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/images/icon.png">
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="nav-wrap">
    <a class="brand" href="index.html">
      <img src="assets/images/icon.png" alt="Time Investment Advisers icon">
      <div>
        <div class="brand-title">Time Investment Advisers LLC</div>
        <div class="brand-sub">Independent Investment Advisory Services</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="index.html" class="">Home</a>
      <a href="about.html" class="">About</a>
      <a href="services.html" class="">Services</a>
      <a href="disclosures.html" class="active">Disclosures</a>
      <a href="contact.html" class="">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>


<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <h1>Disclosures</h1>
    <p>
      Important information about this website, registration status, and the nature of advisory services.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>General disclosure</h3>
    <div class="info-list">
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Registration</div>
        <div><p>Time Investment Advisers LLC is a registered investment adviser in the State of New Jersey. Registration does not imply a certain level of skill or training.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Website purpose</div>
        <div><p>This website is provided for informational purposes only and should not be interpreted as personalized investment, legal, accounting, or tax advice.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Availability</div>
        <div><p>Advisory services are only offered where the firm is properly registered or otherwise exempt from registration requirements.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Risk</div>
        <div><p>All investments involve risk, including the possible loss of principal. Past performance is not indicative of future results.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-tight">
  <div class="notice">
    Before publishing, add your Form ADV Part 2A link and verify that all disclosures, fee descriptions, and advisory language on this website match your current regulatory filings and client documents.
  </div>
</section>


<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-top">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <img src="assets/images/icon.png" alt="Time Investment Advisers logo icon">
        <div>
          <div><strong>Time Investment Advisers LLC</strong></div>
          <div class="footer-note">Independent investment advisory services</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-note">timeinvestmentadvisers@gmail.com</div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-note">
      This website is for informational purposes only and does not constitute an offer to sell or a solicitation of an offer to buy any security or advisory service. Advisory services are only offered where the firm is properly registered or exempt from registration requirements.
    </div>
    <div class="footer-note" style="margin-top:12px;">© 2026 Time Investment Advisers LLC. All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
